cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR

The paper is about deep learning-based classification of HEp-2 cell patterns in images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The methods discussed in the paper involve the use of deep neural networks, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of various datasets, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
